16 SECTION 4. IC 13-26-10-0.5 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA
17 CODE AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS
18 [EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 0.5. (a) A district created after
19 June 30, 2026, may not incur any indebtedness under this chapter
20 without first obtaining the approval of the county fiscal body in
